        <updateDate>2022-11-25T12:37:47Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p>This bill establishes an official policy of the Department of Veterans Affairs (VA) on medicinal cannabis, requires the VA to seek to enter an agreement with a federally funded research and development center to conduct nationwide surveys to measure cannabis use by veterans, and requires the VA to provide training for all VA primary care providers in the use of medical cannabis.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
